Package org.conqat.lib.simulink.builder

This package contains classes that build the SimulinkModel from the MDL file.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ModelBuildingParameters
    Parameter class that controls how certain cases during model building should be handled.
    SimulinkModelBuilder
    Main Simulink/Stateflow model building class.
    SimulinkModelDataExtractor
    Adds MatData and Resources (such as images) to a SimulinkModel.
    SimulinkRegistry
    The Simulink registry is used to parse the XML files loaded at startup and store them in the format of lookup maps.
    SLXDefaultHandlerBase
    Default handler for XML files from slx simulink files.
    SLXModelHandler
    SAX handler for building MutableMDLSection from an .slx file.
    SLXModelSanitizer
    Helper class to sanitize a model created in the new SLX file format to match the MDL file format.
    SLXStateflowHandler
    SAX handler for building MutableMDLSection from the stateflox XML in an SLX file.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    MDLParserException
    Exception thrown by the MDL parser.
    SimulinkModelBuildingException
    This class signals an exception that occurred during build of the Simulink model.

Package org.conqat.lib.simulink.builder Description

This package contains classes that build the SimulinkModel from the MDL file. The entry point is class SimulinkModelBuilder.
